modName: Better Female Khajiit Nude Texture UNP
summary: Makes female Khajiit girly parts look better.
descriptionHtml:
This texture mod alters the female Khajiit genitalia to make it match the more detailed, prettier non-beast race textures. Also, the seem through the middle is now less visible, but the ones on the legs were virtually impossible for me to remove.

Note: Although it is made for UNP, it may work with other body mods. As always, be sure to make backups of the files it replaces if you try it with non-UNP mods.

Updates:
Version 1.1b - Added a new alternate texture, Totally Tucked, for any who prefer it that way.Â 
Version 1.1 - Added by request. Higher definition femalebody.dds and smoother femalebody_msn.dds files eliminate some of the blockiness.

Requirements:

DIMONIZED UNP base
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/6709/?

UNP Khajiit Hotfix
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/11400/?


Very greatly recommended:

CoverKhajiits
http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/5941/?
